Privacy Policy (Text translated into English)
User information to be acquired
AOTAKA STUDIO's apps may collect user information in a form that does not identify individuals.
Our studio uses Google LLC's Firebase and Google Analytics to verify and analyze information, and AdMob and other services for monetization.
You can view the privacy policies of each service by following the website links in the relevant sections.
Purpose of use
· To make it useful for improvement and development etc. of our application
· Analysis of our application usage
· For advertisement display or advertisement
· To use for marketing
· For the purpose attached to the above purpose of use
Handling of personal information
User information is only retrieved in a format that does not identify you within the app.
We will not disclose personally identifiable information to third parties.
Personal information obtained when making inquiries to our company will not be used for any purpose other than contacting us.
Contact information
AOTAKA STUDIO
http://aotaka.sakuratan.com
